0 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Noob gear post. (i *did* search first :P)</span><hr size=1> Get some decent focus items... makes up for it<br>Blackened Alloy Medallion +5 wis -10 mana for all spells  (350) until level 49!  Great investment that starts working from day one.  There are some damageadd level 1's that are attainable (no level2 that I've found)... DoT focus items are easy to get (but I don't rot... so I can't help you there)... you also can get some of the improved heal cheap (turtle hat).<br><br>Wis / Mana super twinks suck... because your meditation isn't up so it takes SOOO long to get your mana back when oom.  So you want items to make it so you don't need to use as much mana.<br><br>+hp items are good<br>+ac items are better<br><br><br>Consider going tunure as a god... then get him a root pendent.  Look around for it...  I do'nt have it so I can't tell you what parts are nodrop... but you can probably do most of it grouped... and keep your druid hiding... then run in to get the item.<br><br><br>Good weapon... I got a good 1hs that looks like a claw!  I can't remember the name... but if you search you will find it... it was 200pp or so.<br><br><br> <p><a><img src="http://www.ergotech-usa.com/~drake/wolf_s.jpg" border="0"></a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ugilth.showPublicProfile?language=EN>gilth</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/globalBlack.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Just got my shots!</span><br>  Posts: 152<br> <font color=#333399>(7/12/02 1:40:13 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26427.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Noob gear post. (i *did* search first :P