Nasthar Vambraces, dunno where they drop, cost 500pp on Fennin<br><br>Othimur Fur Cap  6wis and othr stats , made from tailoring using the furs from otters in CS cost is like 600pp or Nightshade Wreath but i dunno where it drops<br><br>Velium Ruby Veil  8str 8wis <br><br>I know i missed a few spots , thats decent low lvl WIS twink gear. the result should be halfway decent wis above 170 somewhere but crappy hps/ac from gear. You could always lvl it up to liek 25 or so then attempt to run it to UP and with a good 55+ group farm elysian . That gear has insane stats and is a common drop, will yeild good hps/ac/wis but th emobs have 20khps and dbl hit for 200+. a slower , cleric , good tank and a damage dealer can do them all day <br><br> <br><br> <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140031">Stell</a> Ahstellah  <BR>55 Preserver of HOK </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthedruidsgrove.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=fyyrlustorm>FyyrLuStorm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Small Pissed Off Diety<br>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 67<br> <font color=#333399>(7/15/02 5:51:47 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=26427.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> RE:</span><hr size=1> I got an RMB off a normal kobold up at the top of Sol, long ago.<br><br>Did someone spike his loot?<br><br>Must have. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showPrevMessage?topicID=26427.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showNextMessage?topicID=26427.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br>